caption: Pray for Paris......this is really sad..never expected this to happen but.......most things happen unexpectedly....this tragedy has killed so many people......what do terrorists get by killing people...man killing man....totally wrong.....I hope and pray that this never happens and I wish God gives the power to the families who have gone through this and the people who have lost their lives......should rest in peace...my prayers will be there with France and the families for now and forever......please if you are reading this don't forget to do a small prayer as even a single prayer is so powerful that it can change it into a miracle????
song_title: A Dream Is a Wish Your Heart Makes
